# Yappie-Yappie

Welcome!

I am building this to explore new things and also making a chatting space which currently is exclusive only to me and my best friends, where we make groups and chat together.

Though there are already existing apps, this will be exclusive only to us.

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- Node.js
- Express
- MongoDB (Mongoose)
- React (Vite)
- Socket.IO
- Tailwind CSS

---

## 📁 Project Structure

yappieyappie/
├── server/ → backend (Express + MongoDB + Socket.IO)
└── client/ → frontend (React + Tailwind + Socket.IO-client)